Text: Vision Valuesa word of thanks to Enron for its Vision Values I have just read them again and found them up lifting I am writing you because prior to working for Enron Ken Lay and Enron were synonymous I had not known the value and respect that Enron had for its employees Great belief Thanks again for the words of encouragement Vision Values Winifred Flix Isaac X
